{"tid":2275824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★資金偷步入市　美股基金單周吸資842億","createTime":"2020-11-07T12:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T12:35:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0615ef7e446d614284069ea926daef6cba0d98ba","tid":2275824,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"美國總統大選雖然未有最終結果，但資金似乎已偷步入市！據美國銀行引述EPFR資金流數字顯示，截至周三(4日)止1周，美股基金吸資18億美元(約842億美元)，3周以來首錄資金流入。當中，美國小型股基金吸資19億美元，大型股基金則錄得19億美元資金流出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201107/bkn-20201107153644199-1107_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201107%2Fbkn-20201107153644199-1107_00842_001.html&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=d1ae0eda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201107/bkn-20201107153644199-1107_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"39ef2288bebaf4aafe27cf579c59f0316615818a","tid":2275824,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cf168f71ee86b03eb9f624c9f14a92812e542c","tid":2275824,"uid":73856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"美股基金吸資18億美元(約842億美元)"},{"pid":"6ace2d7b890f35bcc2f407eaeec1d82120cd3bcd","tid":2275824,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"唔怪得係咁升<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}